overview: The second installment in a multivolume series, this collection of memorable vintage performance clips and music videos provides the ultimate reggae concert experience -- and now, lucky you have the combination to the vault! With sizzling sets from some of the most popular reggae artists in the industry, the all-star lineup includes Sugar Minott, Eric Donaldson and the legendary dancehall master Yellowhall.
title: Sessions from the Vault: Vol. 2
